# Concise Formatting Rules cho Product Designer

## Content Structure - 80/20 Principle
- **Maximum efficiency**: 500 lines per rule file (focus vào essential information)
- **Hierarchical organization**: Clear section headers với logical flow cho easy scanning
- **Strategic bullet points**: Sử dụng bullet points cho lists và specifications (easier to digest)
- **Code blocks**: Include code examples với proper syntax highlighting khi necessary
- **Visual tables**: Sử dụng tables cho structured data comparison (designer-friendly)

## Writing Guidelines - Clear Communication
- **Eliminate redundancy**: Remove unnecessary repetition (respect reader's time)
- **Active voice**: Direct và actionable language (faster comprehension)
- **Specific details**: Include exact values và parameters khi relevant
- **Logical flow**: Organize information theo logical sequence (problem → solution)
- **Consistent terminology**: Sử dụng uniform naming conventions (avoid confusion)

## Format Standards - Professional Presentation
- **Markdown formatting**: Consistent markdown formatting cho all documentation
- **Structured data**: JSON/YAML cho configuration data với proper indentation
- **Inline comments**: Concise code comments cho implementation details
- **Reference links**: Relevant links to related documentation và resources
- **Version tracking**: Include version information cho tracking changes

## Efficiency Principles cho Product Designer
- **One concept per section**: Focus trên single topic (clear mental models)
- **Immediate applicability**: Provide actionable information (can implement right away)
- **Visual hierarchy**: Use headers, bold, italics để create visual structure
- **Cross-references**: Link related concepts và files (efficient navigation)
- **Standardized templates**: Consistent structure (predictable format)

## Vietnamese Content Guidelines
- **Primary language**: Tiếng Việt cho main communication
- **Technical terms**: Giữ nguyên technical terminology tiếng Anh
- **Clear explanations**: Explain complex concepts bằng tiếng Việt với examples
- **Mixed usage**: Natural mixing của Vietnamese và English technical terms
- **Accessibility**: Ensure content accessible cho Vietnamese-speaking designers

## Quality Metrics - Measurable Standards
- **Readability**: Clear và understandable content (scan-friendly)
- **Completeness**: All necessary information included (no critical gaps)
- **Accuracy**: Precise và correct technical details (reliable reference)
- **Maintainability**: Easy to update và modify (sustainable documentation)
- **Reusability**: Applicable across multiple contexts (efficient reuse)

## Document Organization Patterns
- **Quick reference**: Start với key information cho immediate needs
- **Detailed sections**: Follow với comprehensive details cho deep dives
- **Examples**: Include practical examples cho better understanding
- **Troubleshooting**: Common issues và solutions (problem-solving focus)
- **Resources**: Links to additional resources cho extended learning

## Content Optimization Strategies
- **Progressive disclosure**: Present information theo increasing detail levels
- **Scannable format**: Use formatting để support quick scanning
- **Action-oriented**: Focus trên what readers need to do
- **Context-aware**: Provide appropriate context cho decision making
- **Visual elements**: Use formatting elements để enhance comprehension

